list.name: Default
list.comment: Designed all pages for the checkout view. Added a CheckoutController handle in the IMatController (copy the getController line to add handles for other controllers). Cleaned up some unnecessary files.

task.summary: Added the top toolbar without functionality. Added css-file.
Added functionality for switching views using the top toolbar, and renamed some things.
Cleaned fxml files and added skeleton files for some views, controllers and a logo. All views now work.
Designed the initial history view. Added a DisabledSelectionModel for lists where the items shouldn't be selectable.
Designed and implemented most of the detailed view for history. TODO: Create custom table view
Created custom tableview for history detailed view.
Added highlight for the selected view in the top toolbar. Designed a prototype custom grid for the home view, currently implemented in the checkout view.
Created the first page of the checkoutView. Standardized some css and fixed some layout bugs. Changed the standard price format from "xx.xx :-" to "xx,xx kr".
